FAQ

Have a question?

Does AtoB file 1099 forms?

Yes, within your Driver Pay dashboard you can access 1099 forms.

Does AtoB offer W2s?

AtoB does not currently support W2 payroll.

How fast is Driver Pay?

Funds almost always arrive in 30 minutes or less, usually less than 2 minutes.

How do you qualify for Driver Pay?

All AtoB customers with a credit fuel card product qualify for Driver Pay from the day they are approved. AtoB customers with a prepaid fuel card product only qualify for Driver Pay if they've been in business for at least two years and have been an AtoB customer for at least 90 days.
